svg.title: Sharif University of Technology logo
svg.desc: This is a redesign of Sharif University of Technology's logo, which improves on existing versions. The work was performed by Hamed Amanollahi and supervised by Pooria Soltani at the International Affairs Office, Sharif University of Technology, 2021. The HEX color code of the design is #1966AB, which is the year of establishment of the university, and the color blue in Farsi (Abi).
